蹤男子（曾秋文攝）<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名死者疑是23歲朱植雄失蹤男子，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他於前日（9日）上午離開其位於秀明道的住所後便告失蹤</span></strong></span>，其家人同日向警方報案。他身高約1.78米，體重約68公斤，肥身材、圓面型、黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮。他最後露面時身穿白色背心、紅色短褲及深色拖鞋。<br />\n<br />\n9號喎 關831同新屋嶺咩事？"},{"pid":"6c21cda8e40ff37aa4208cf1cf3f8deef65153bf","tid":1562464,"uid":321357,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf988d1bb9d6dda94f8b3b141ac5d52200d9d3c7","tid":1562464,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:58:19.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪邨發現一名男死者伏屍天井 為失蹤者朱植雄<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2449252/%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E9%82%A8%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BC%8F%E5%B1%8D%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E3%80%80%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E8%80%85%E6%9C%B1%E6%A4%8D%E9%9B%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2449252%2F%25E7%25A7%2580%25E8%258C%2582%25E5%259D%25AA%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BC%258F%25E5%25B1%258D%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BA%2595%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%25B1%25E6%25A4%258D%25E9%259B%2584&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=a990ee9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2449252/%E7%A7%80%E8%8C%82%E5%9D%AA%E9%82%A8%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%94%B7%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BC%8F%E5%B1%8D%E5%A4%A9%E4%BA%95%E3%80%80%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E8%80%85%E6%9C%B1%E6%A4%8D%E9%9B%84</a><br />\n<br />\n早上11時許，警方接報秀茂坪邨秀義樓有一名年約20多歲男子倒伏在大廈1樓天井位置，警方及消防到場，消防員到男子伏屍位置，證實明顯死亡，毋須送院；但由於救出困難，消防要派出升降梯協助將死者遺體由天井抬出再運至地面；警方經調查，初步認為無可疑，暫列屍體發現。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ab4227ec52ac5efbf0d233e2f43fb7248a2a14","tid":1562464,"uid":92832,"like":0,"dislike":